%center%To use this help system, you may use PgUp and PgDn keys to page though
%center%the different help screens.  Also, a help page might have "hot links"
%center%to other help screens.  These will be shown by having certain key words
%center%and phrases in highlighted lettering.  There will be also a "light bar"
%center%which you can move (using , , , , Tab, Shift-Tab, or Spacebar) to
%center%highlight the hot link of your choice at which point you may press Enter
%center%to jump to that help screen.


